  "description": "Adds security features to Minecraft",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'arial black', sans-serif;\">--- Security Features ---</span></p>\nFor previous versions go here: https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/security-features-ioi\n\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;\">The Security Features mod is a mod that will increase security in your base and help you keep any nasty players out. What we give you:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;\">Laser Blocks</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;\">Laser Crystals &amp; Ore</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;\">+ More!</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;\">Laser blocks deal damage when touched by the player</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;\">You use Laser crystals to craft Laser crystal blocks then turn them into laser blocks</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;\">This is a VERY small project so far</span>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;\">Made with MCreator</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;\">Project Status: Early Dev</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;IOI stands for: Internet Over Internals</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n